Dialogs.Dialog: Sensei
Now, the next question...
(Urgh... Our eyes met.)
Right, can you try it？
Good. Well done.
(I'm glad I studied before- hand...)
You should have studied properly beforehand.
(Maybe it's a good idea to study harder...)
Sensei
Okay, today we'll be having a quiz.
(This is a bit sudden... Will I be okay？)
(I did well. I'm glad I studied beforehand...)
(That was awful. I should have studied more...)
(We'll be having a match during P.E. class today.)
P.E. Sensei
Ready？ Set. Go！
Guy A
That was great. You did very well.
(I'm glad I've exercised regularly...)
Hey！ Can't you be a bit more serious！？
(I should exercise more regularly...)
P.E. sensei
Today, we will have a physical strength test！
(It's sudden... Will I be okay？)
Good. You passed！
(I'm glad I've been exercising regularly...)
Hey, what's wrong？ Can't you even move your body！？
(I should've exercised more...)
Music sensei
Okay, today I'll test everyone's practical skill.
(Skill？ Will I be okay？)
Yes. Wonderfully done.
(It's good that I've been working on my sense.)
Hmm... You'll have to try harder next time, okay？
(I should've worked on my sense a bit more...)
Art sensei
Okay, everyone. You will have to present your work in front of the class today.
(I wonder if this will be okay...)
Wonderful！ You possess such great sense.
(It's good that I've been working on my sense.)
This is... I'm trying to figure out its artistic merit, but...
(I should've worked on my sense a bit more...)
Guy A
Hey, you. You've been quite popular lately.
Is that so？
Guy B
Yeah, yeah. Earlier, a girl from another class asked me about you.
Geez. I'm so jealous.
(Maybe it's because I've been paying attention to my appearance and behavior, huh？)
Hey, you... You don't seem to be very popular lately.
Really！？
I guess. The girls are gossiping about you.
I think it's better if you try to do something with yourself.
(Is that so？ I think I should pay more attention to my appearance and how I behave...)
Girl A
Hey, hey. You're quite popular, you know？
Is that so？
Girl B
Yeah, us girls talk about you a lot.
That's great, isn't it？
(Maybe it's because I've been paying attention to my appearance and behavior, huh？)
You... Lately, you've been so unpopular.
Is this true！？
Yeah, there are bad rumors about you as well...
You'd better watch out, okay？
(Is that so？ I think I should pay more attention to my appearance and how I behave...)
Sensei
You've been working hard lately, eh？
Do you really think so？
Yes, even other senseis have mentioned you and said that you're diligent. Keep it up, okay？
(I see. It's good to be careful with my behavior.)
Hey, you... Can you take things more seriously？
Eh！？
I've heard bad things about you from other senseis as well. You'd better clean up your act.
(Really？ I should be more careful from now on...)
Member
Hey, there's something I didn't understand when I was studying. Mind if I ask you？
No problem...
(I hope it'll be okay...)
Thank you！ You really saved me. You know your stuff pretty well, huh？
(Good thing I studied regularly...)
What is this...？ You're unreliable, you know？ I'll go ask someone else.
(...Maybe it would have been a good idea to study a little more...)
Member
Hey, hey. Did you watch that match？ It was awesome.
Um...
I know, right？ No way he could've returned it from there.
(I'm glad we could chat like this. Good thing I was well prepared...)
What？ You didn't watch it？ Well, that's okay... Ah！ Did you watch that match？
(I guess I should've paid closer attention...)
Captain
That's the end of today's practice！
Hah, today was tiring...
Member
Good work！ You were really active out there today. Keep it up.
(I guess that's the fruit of my labor...)
Thanks for trying out there today, but were you feeling sick or something？
(I should've practiced a bit more, huh...)
Manager
Today, we have practice matches within the club！
(It's only a practice match among members, but I should still do my best.)
(All right！ I won！)
Member
Ah, I lost. Next time, the victory's mine！
(I lost...)
All right. Today, the victory's mine！
Advisor
How's everything going？
Well...
Yeah, it looks like you're practicing the basics properly.
(I guess it's the result of regular practice...)
...Looks like you'd better start from the basics.
(I guess I'll have to practice more, huh...)
(Well then, it's practice time...)
Member
Ah, that thing you're wearing...
This？
It's only just come out and you already got one？ You are so lucky....
(It's good that I follow the latest trends...)
Hey, that thing you're wearing...
You mean this？
Isn't that kind of out of style？ I guess it's okay, but...
(Maybe I should pay more attention to fashion...)
Advisor
Oh, working hard, eh？
Sensei...
Yeah, you seem to have good senses.
Sense？ Meaning...
The basics are physical strength and practice. But in a match, sense is also essential. You've done pretty well.
(I see...)
Hmm, your senses might be lacking.
Sense...？
The basics are physical strength and practice. But sense can influence a match too. It's difficult to win without sense.
(Sense, huh...？)
Member
You've gotten more popular lately.
You really think so？
Yeah. You stand out as a reliable guy.
(I wonder if it's because I'm being careful about my looks and behavior...)
Hey... I've heard a lot of bad things about you lately.
Really！？
People say you're not reliable and you don't stand out. I don't agree, but...
(Really？ I should've paid more attention to my looks and behavior...)
Advisor
Lately, it seems like you have been taking practice more seriously.
You think so？
Yeah. It seems your enthusiasm has inspired the other members, too.
(Really？ I wonder if it's because I've been careful about my behavior...)
Hey, you... Can't you take practice a little more seriously？
Eh！？
You're being a burden to the other members. At least try harder, okay？
(Really... I guess I should have tried to pay more attention to my behavior...)
Girl
Um, there's a book that I'm looking for...
Okay...
It's this one, right？
Thanks for helping me out.
(Good thing I've studied this stuff regularly...)
Let's see... Where was it again...？
Enough. I'll look for it myself...
(...Maybe I should have studied a bit more...)
Today I have to organize the bookshelves...
Memorizing the library's classification system beforehand paid off.
I didn't really understand how to classify the books, so I had a hard time...
These books have to be placed on the other side.
There are quite a few. Can I carry all of them in one go？
Whew, just like this.
Whoa！
Good thing I was able to carry them all without hurting myself...
Now then, today's agenda is cleaning the shelves...
All right, it's a lot cleaner now.
Whoa！
*sigh* If I don't sort them out again...
That reminds me. Earlier, I recommended some books... I wonder what they thought of them.
People borrowed them... Somehow, that makes me happy.
No one borrowed them. What a failed attempt.
That reminds me. Earlier, I wrote a book review. I wonder how it was received...
I'll just take a peek in the survey box...
"I tried reading the book. The contents lived up to my expectations. I'll eagerly await for the next recommendation."
Looks like my sense has been recognized. I'm glad.
"I tried reading the book, but it didn't live up to my expectations. Please don't post misleading book reviews."
I wonder if my sense is strange...
Advisor
The books you helped us order seem to be very popular.
Is that so？
Yes, they're appropriate for a school library, and the contents appear to be very interesting.
(Guess that means my sense has been recognized...)
Ah, the books you helped us order last time... They're a bit...
Eh！？
They're not appropriate for a school library. We'll have to send them back...
(Really？ I guess my sense is a bit off...)
Girl
Um, I'd like to borrow this book...
Okay...
Okay, here you go.
Thank you very much, for patiently helping me...
No problem. Here you go.
...Somehow, I don't enjoy being here...
(Ah... Should I have been more careful...？)
(Now then, there's a committee meeting today.)
Advisor
The library committee has been very helpful by working diligently.
(I wonder if it's thanks to my usual actions...)
Although this is only a school committee, I hope that you can all be a bit more diligent.
(I'll have to be more careful...)
Guest
Check, please.
Yes, one moment please.
(They ordered so many extra dishes... and they canceled this one... What a pain.)
Thank you very much.
I'll come back later.
(I'm glad I'm well prepared...)
Hm... What do I do with this...？
Girl
Hey, hurry up. If you can't then just ask someone else to do it.
(I should've learned to do this in advance.)
Ah, today we started using a new menu.
Before work starts, I should make sure to go over the new menu items.
All right, I remember all of them.
This isn't good. I can't remember any of them and my shift is about to start...
There are a lot of dishes. I have to carry them all at once...
Handling this much is no problem for me.
Ah！
Geez, I guess it was impossible...
Well, it's my turn to sweep the floor today.
Okay, I guess that's it.
Ah！
Ah... I've got to tidy up...
Manager
Hey, you. This is from our new menu. Can you try it and give me your opinion？
Sure...
If you cook it that way, I think it will taste better.
I see. You're really helpful. Thanks.
(I'm glad I've been heightening my senses lately.)
....That's what I think. Something like that...
I don't quite get it. I'll ask some of the other staff to taste it then.
(I should've polished my sense...)
Manager
Ah, you. For the coming fair, could you take care of the display？
Okay. I got it.
Oh, wonderful. I'm glad I asked you to do this.
(I'm glad I've been heightening my senses lately.)
This is... You must do something with it, or...
(I should've polished my sense...)
Customer
Ah, waiter！
Yes. I'll be right there.
Thank you. You are so helpful.
(I think it's good to be attentive...)
Hey, the service here is pretty bad.
(Argh... I must be more attentive...)
Manager
Ah, you. Our customers have praised you for your good service, you know？
Really？
Yeah. Please keep up the good work.
(I'm glad everything's going well...)
You... You know, we've had some complaints about your service.
I'm very sorry...
You must be more careful from now on.
(Oh no. I'll have to be really careful.)
(All right. Time to work...)
Manager
Oh, you always look clean and tidy. Keep it up.
(I'm glad I dressed myself well...)
You... Be more mindful of your appearance. Being clean is very important.
(I'll have to be careful about how I look.)
Come to think of it... midterms are coming soon.
I'd better study in advance...
Okay, today's the midterm exam. I'll try to do my best...
It's finally over...
All that's left to do is to wait for the results.
Come to think of it... the final exams are coming up.
I'd better study in advance...
Now then, today's the final exam. I'll have to do my best.
It's finally over...
All that's left to do is to wait for the results.
Come to think of it... the sports festival is coming up soon.
It might be a bit late, but I'd better start training...
Come to think of it... the music contest is coming up soon.
It might be a bit late, but I'd better start refining my music sense...
The music contest is today.
I'll just try to do what I can...
Yes！ I won a prize！
It's probably because I've been working hard to improve recently.
I couldn't win a prize. Well, whatever...
Come to think of it, a picture I drew in art class was submitted to a contest...
The results will be out soon. I wonder how it will turn out.
Seems like the art contest results are out.
Will my work be there...？
There it is！ I won！
It's probably because I've been working hard to improve recently.
No, it's not. Well, whatever...
The culture festival is coming up soon.
Come to think of it... There's a "Handsome Man" contest during the culture festival.
I don't really care about it... Or do I？
Come to think of it... the sports festival is coming up soon.
I have to participate in the school support battle. I wonder if I can do that well...
Well, next up is the support battle. I'll do my best！
Yes！ In the end, our team won the first prize！
It's not my day...
Come to think of it... We will have practice matches with other schools soon.
Should I start to focus on more intense training？
We will have a practice match with another school today. I'll do my best.
Yeah！ I won！
I'll keep it up and do better next time.
I lost...
I have to practice harder...
Speaking of which, an official match is coming up soon...
I should spend more time practicing.
Today is the deadline for submitting an essay for the criticism contest.
I believe I did the best I could. Now I just have to wait for the results.
I think the results from the criticism contest should be out...
Ah, yes！ I won an award！
I'm glad I worked hard on writing the essay.
Nope, my name wasn't even listed...
I'll have to do better than this...
By the way, people from headquarters will come to check on us today.
They will be evaluating us for the national model employee award as well....
Is it possible that I might be nominated, too？
That reminds me, the results from the model employee award are out...
Ah！ It's my name！
I'm glad I've been serious at work.
I wasn't chosen. Well, no surprise there...
